\pard\sa115\sl-275\li115 \b\fs24 Game Menu Commands\plain\fs24 
\par \pard\sa35\sl-235\li115 \b\fs20 Hint\plain\fs20 
\par \pard\sl-235\li115 Suggests a move for you.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115 When you choose Hint, a cross appears over the square the computer would choose if it were its turn to play. You can accept the suggestion or move elsewhere.
\par \pard\sb235\sa35\sl-235\li115 \b Pass\plain\fs20 
\par \pard\sl-235\li115 Skips your turn, giving the move to the computer.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115 You can choose Pass on your first move to force the computer to make the first play. After that, you can only choose Pass when you cannot make a legal move.
\par \pard\sb235\sa35\sl-235\li115 \b New\plain\fs20 
\par \pard\sl-235\li115 Starts a new game.
\par \pard\sb75\sl-235\li115 You can start a new game at any time, even before you finish a game.
\par \pard\sb235\sa35\sl-235\li115 \b Exit\plain\fs20 
\par \pard\sl-235\li115 Exits Reversi.
