\pard\sa115\sl-275\li115 \b\fs24 Rules of the Game\plain\fs24 
\par \pard\sa35\sl-235\li115 \b\fs20 Rules of Reversi:\plain\fs20 
\par \pard\sl-235\li355\fi-235\tx355 1\tab You and the computer play by the same rules.
\par \pard\sb55\sl-235\li355\fi-235\tx355 2\tab To make a legal move, you must choose a square in which the pointer changes to a cross.
\par 3\tab You can choose Pass on your first move to force the computer to play first.
\par 4\tab After your first move, you cannot pass if you can make a legal move.
\par 5\tab If you cannot make a legal move, you must choose Pass from the Game menu.
\par 6\tab When neither you nor the computer can make a move, the game is over.
\par 7\tab The one with the most circles wins.
